My-XBMEditor version  3.0
=========================

XBM is an old monochrome graphic format. It's so old that modern
graphics software do not support it anymore.
Luckily someone at Perlmonks wrote such an XBM editor in Perl/Tk.

This package provides the XBM editor.

INSTALLATION

Get Perl.

Install this module and run xbm-editor in the bin folder.

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

See the Makefile for dependencies.

